reviews.text: Was nice food, hot and seemed fresh. I went with a large group of people 11+ and it was a good experience. They were very accomodating. Would go again.
Expensive pizza and drinks compared with Australian prices. Good service and clean rest rooms.
This branch is very clean and quite located in upper floor. However, the quality of food is average even though it comes hot. The service is okay but not the best.
We ate a 2person set that day with salted eggs recipe. My friend and I found the texture interesting and refreshing. Point to note is that the amount is quite large. Dont overestimate yourself!
Delicious pizzas. They were juicy and nice unlike the Indian version of the same franchise.

reviews.text: Was nice food, hot and seemed fresh. I went with a large group of people 11+ and it was a good experience. They were very accomodating. Would go again.
出品味道不及西九龍中心分店好，但服務可加分。
Expensive pizza and drinks compared with Australian prices. Good service and clean rest rooms.
食物OK但無驚喜，價錢貴貴哋但可接受，唯一個別員工 服務麻麻地，黑口黑面，粗聲粗氣。 其實附近仲有其他 類似的選擇未必會返去幫襯

Solita pizza, più che sopportabile quando si è all' estero e si desidera una tregua dal cibo locale. Consiglio per gli Italiani: scegliete la pasta alta con pomodoro e mozzarella. Qualsiasi variante allontana inesorabilmente il sapore da quello della nostra pizza.
